OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight frost and fog
OL,6,Fwill soon clear to leave plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine to start with on Sunday.
OL,8,FCloud will slowly bubble up during the
OL,9,Fmorning, limiting the sunshine this
OL,10,Fafternoon, though staying largely dry.
OL,11,FLighter winds than recently.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe fine weather will
OL,14,Fcontinue this evening and overnight.
OL,15,FThere will be sunny spells to end the
OL,16,Fday, with clear spells and light winds
OL,17,Fovernight. Some frost in rural areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
